SUMMARY:Awards Night at Rialto Cinemas Sebastopol
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T150000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260315T190000
UID:c5863c90c61fd05cf13df66db397a263@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:Have you ever experienced Hollywood’s biggest night with an 
 audience? Join us as we raise funds for Food for Thought and enjoy an even
 ing of stargazing\, suspense\, and prizes! Food For Thought is a nonprofit
  organization providing healthy groceries\, meals\, and loving support to 
 people living with serious medical conditions in Sonoma County—all free 
 of charge. Tickets are $49 and include food\, beverages\, games\, trivia\,
  prizes\, and costume contest—bring your best Hollywood glam or movie-th
 emed looks. Catering provided by Field & Farm. Tickets and info at RIALTOC
 INEMAS.com Red Carpet 3:00 pm | Show Begins 4:00 pm
LOCATION:Petaluma\, CA
URL:https://business.petalumachamber.us/events/details/awards-night-at-ria
 lto-cinemas-sebastopol
X-SOURCE:Petaluma Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:The Great Literacy Adventure
DTSTART;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T110000
DTEND;TZID=PDT;VALUE=DATE-TIME:20260411T150000
UID:926f6c81a02c3ceb0b0b7fa2ff22e264@growthzone.com
DESCRIPTION:The Great Literacy Adventure is a free\, countywide celebratio
 n of literacy and lifelong learning highlighting the Sonoma County Literac
 y Promise. This event is hosted by Sonoma County Office of Education and N
 orthern California Public Media. It brings together families\, educators\,
  Sonoma County Literacy Partners and dynamic literacy advocates to champio
 n joyful\, inclusive literacy activities and connect families with resourc
 es countywide to promote literacy at home. Come for part or stay for the w
 hole event! Audience: Families with children\, educators\, and community p
 artners from Sonoma County (All children must be accompanied by an adult) 
 Parking: Free at the neighboring Rohnert Park Kaiser Permanente Building l
 ocated at 5900 State Farm Drive.
LOCATION:Petaluma\, CA
URL:https://business.petalumachamber.us/events/details/the-great-literacy-
 adventure
X-SOURCE:Petaluma Chamber of Commerce
END:VEVENT
